    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="node-dot"></span> MY STORY</div>
      <h2 style="font-size: clamp(24px,3vw,30px); margin-bottom:16px;">From computer science to entity-first SEO</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:18px;">I'm Manish Ghimire, originally from Tansen, Palpa, and now based in Balaju, Kathmandu. I hold a Bachelor in Computer Application (BCA) from Ratna Rajyalaxmi Campus, Tribhuwan University, which gave me the technical foundation, databases, web development, systems thinking, that now shapes how I approach SEO.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:18px;">Over the past two years at RankMeTop, I've grown from SEO Intern to SEO Team Lead, working across 50+ projects spanning legal, SaaS, eCommerce, home services, finance and more. Along the way I built a strong focus on semantic SEO, EEAT, and topical authority, sharpened by studying Koray Tugberk Gubur's topical authority methodology in depth.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:32px;">I believe good SEO isn't about gaming an algorithm, it's about structuring a site the way search engines are actually built to understand: as a network of entities, relationships, and intent. That's the lens I bring to every audit, every content brief, and every technical fix.</p>

      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="node-dot"></span> HOW I WORK</div>
      <div class="grid cols-2" style="margin-top:8px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Entity &amp; Topical Strategy</h3>
          <p>Topical maps, content clusters and EAV-driven coverage that build genuine subject authority.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Technical Rigor</h3>
          <p>Full technical audits, crawling, indexing, Core Web Vitals, structured data, fixed at the source.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Data-Backed Decisions</h3>
          <p>Every recommendation traced back to Search Console, GA4, or a documented hypothesis test.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>AI Search Ready</h3>
          <p>Structuring content so brands surface in Google AI Overviews, ChatGPT, Gemini and Perplexity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

